    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>zingy salad</strong> topped with the <strong>pulled chicken </strong>and garnish with the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>coriander leaves </strong>– this is your<strong> Indian-style chicken breast salad with spicy green chutney</strong></p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>nigella seeds </strong>over the top</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
